channel.title: Is this normal?
channel.description:
Hi, this is not really for help but it is a question on an error I frequently get on higher revision servers.
Alright. So I keep getting the following messages when I run the server. NOTE: I know how to fix these, they are very easy to fix, but I am just wondering if they are normal and if you guys also get them.
I normally get these on servers 525+:
1. NPC.java does not have a no-args constructor.
2. Item.java does not have a no-args constructor.
3. Location.java does not have a no-args constructor.
4. Player.java does not have a no-args constructor.
Please reply if you have gotten these before because I am wondering whether or not this is normal.
